        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="5J4kaEMYKeDm40zFRqjC-1" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;hachureGap=4;fontFamily=Architects Daughter;fontSource=https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Architects+Daughter;fillColor=light-dark(#FFFFFF,#333333);align=left;spacing=14;" value="&lt;div&gt;ANSWER:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- Love - This is the core&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- Thoughts, Actions and Feelings - These are the use-cases&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- Heart - infrastructure&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- Physical body and manifestation - presentation&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- compositions - consciousness - it helps connect the physical body and manifestation to the heart, via use-cases.&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
